OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780419953
OL,3,C'Oldest' Horizon scandal victim Betty
OL,4,CBrown receives OBE from King
OL,6,FA woman said to be the oldest victim
OL,7,Fof the Post Office Horizon IT scandal
OL,8,Fsaid the King is as "upset" about the
OL,9,Fordeal as the victims after receiving
OL,10,Fher OBE at Windsor Castle today.
OL,12,FBetty Brown, 93, was among 68 people
OL,13,Fto be honoured by the King at Windsor
OL,14,FCastle alongside Luther star Sir Idris
OL,15,FElba and ice skating champions Dame
OL,16,FJayne Torvill and Sir Christopher Dean.
OL,26,@pD@UOUpD@[O]
