PN,42106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780419953
OL,3,C'Oldest' Horizon scandal victim Betty
OL,4,CBrown receives OBE from King
OL,6,FIn a direct appeal to Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer, she asked the Prime Minister
OL,8,Fto resolve the scandal "as quickly as
OL,9,Fyou can".
OL,11,FShe said: "Don't take another 26
OL,12,Fyears, because all you're doing is
OL,13,Fwaiting for the poor souls to die off,
OL,14,Fone-by-one, until there will be no-one
OL,15,Fleft and the case is forgotten about
OL,16,Fin the history books, if it ever makes
OL,17,Fit."
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@HO]sD@KOUyD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
