OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780419953
OL,3,C'Oldest' Horizon scandal victim Betty
OL,4,CBrown receives OBE from King
OL,6,FMs Brown reached a settlement at the
OL,7,Fend of last year through the
OL,8,FGovernment's redress scheme, but said
OL,9,Fshe is yet to receive a "penny" in
OL,10,Fcompensation.
OL,12,FShe said: "I said to the King: 'The
OL,13,Fchildren need our compensation.'
OL,14,FFujitsu are trying to back out now `
OL,15,Fthey're giving the children therapy.
OL,16,FWe don't want therapy, we want money
OL,17,Fto put a roof over their heads and
OL,18,Fgive them what Horizon took away from
OL,19,Fus.
OL,26,@qD@YOUqD@_O]tD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780419953
OL,3,C'Oldest' Horizon scandal victim Betty
OL,4,CBrown receives OBE from King
OL,6,F"They took away our lives, they took
OL,7,Faway our future for our children.
OL,8,FWe've got no money to pass on to the
OL,9,Fchildren ` we would have had if we'd
OL,10,Fcontinued working.
OL,12,F"My children now have that, other
OL,13,Fpeople's children, they don't have
OL,14,Fthat to look forward to. They've got
OL,15,Fno inheritance. We don't want therapy
OL,16,Ffrom Fujitsu. We want pennies from
OL,17,Fthem."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
