OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780419953
OL,3,C'Oldest' Horizon scandal victim Betty
OL,4,CBrown receives OBE from King
OL,6,FAsked how she found the strength to
OL,7,Fcontinue fighting for justice for so
OL,8,Flong, Ms Brown said strength is found
OL,9,Fin the "truth".
OL,11,F"I've never lied about anything," she
OL,12,Fsaid. "I've given them the truth, and
OL,13,Fthe longer you tell the truth, the
OL,14,Fstronger the truth gets."
OL,16,FMs Brown said she will celebrate the
OL,17,Fhonour by enjoying "the love of my
OL,18,Ffamily".
OL,26,@qD@HOUqD@NO]sD@AOUsD@aO]tD@GOUvD@YO]yD@
OL,26,ATOUzD@GO]
